The world is big and I want to have a good look at it before it gets dark.
If I said this Earth was an amber waterfall in which I yearn to embrace each day, would it mean I am closer to knowing something about love?
I thank the Universe for this most amazing day, for the leaping green spirits of trees, for the blue dream of sky, and for everything which is natural, infinite, yes.
It is good to have an end to journey toward, but it is the journey that matters in the end.
In all things of nature there is something of the marvelous.
How glorious a greeting the sun gives the mountains.
You're off to great places! Today is your day! Your mountain is calling... So, get on your way!!
Between every two pines is a doorway to the world.
You're off to great places!  Today is your day!  Your mountain is waiting, so get on your way!!
It's not the years in your life that count, but the life in your years.
If I could live my life again, I'd climb more mountains, I'd watch more sunrises.
